{"tid":1435650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「論大台」菩提本無樹，明鏡亦非台，本來無一物，何處惹塵埃","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:31:54.000Z","uid":114801,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63aa4c07e5a1a8ab33b709e03499a9af1b7a93f5","tid":1435650,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"「身是菩提樹，心為明鏡台。時時勤拂拭，勿使惹塵埃。」<br />\n-告誡群眾要時時刻刻警惕大台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菩提本無樹，明鏡亦非台，本來無一物，何處惹塵埃。」<br />\n-本來就無大台，甚至我地可以連「大台」呢個概念都唔存在時，又何須提防大台？"},{"pid":"011936dd3c139058102af81d0c15f9cddf2443c3","tid":1435650,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}